description: Leaders across the continent are holding closed ceremonies, without the public in attendance.
title: VE Day: Europe marks 75th anniversary amid coronavirus lockdown
title_page: VE Day: Europe marks 75th anniversary amid coronavirus lockdown - BBC News
maintext: France has been under strict lockdown since mid-March, and on Monday the nation begins an eagerly awaited easing of it, though the amount of easing will vary regionally. Paris and the north-east are the virus hotspots.
